descriptionNullable:
Provides data for beginners to implement forecasting models over real world tourist numbers visiting an island. The users can play around with the trend and seasonality components to build a robust model.

**The objective here is to forecast for next subsequent 6 months.**

Please upvote if you find the dataset useful.
